o to india this winter.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;today i did a lot. i slept in the afternoon. i read some other people's blogs and thought about blogging. i tried to get a little work done. i took the dog to the park for a walk. i drank pabst blue ribbon and watched a couple episodes of M.A.S.H. then i decided that i should start another blog. so i am now starting this blog. it has been a super day.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;it is already july fifth. i have a ton of shit to do this summer.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;i may draw some things and post them here.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;this blog will start slowly and then gather momentum.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;yesterday the neighbor invited me to her party on saturday. i might go. she had a kimono on but i don't think she's japanese.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;i may take pictures of my dog and post them here. he is getting on in years and he deserves a shot at fame. maybe i can help.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;i will come up with a better name than deppresiviality. this is still the prototype. i'm okay with that.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;i'm going to go sit on the porch and listen to crickets now.</content><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://blog.allometric.net/2006/07/depressiviality.html' title='depressiviality'/><link rel='replies' type='text/html' href='http://www.blogger.com/comment.g?blogID=30719777&amp;postID=115216711984817888' title='0 Comments'/><link rel='replies' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://blog.allometric.net/feeds/115216711984817888/comments/default' title='Post Comments'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/30719777/posts/default/115216711984817888'/><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/30719777/posts/default/115216711984817888'/><author><name>Greg</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/11511247372356785100</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email></author></entry></feed>